ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該話<br />\n1萬蚊幾實好多人都負擔得起<br />\n但問題係你自己覺得值唔值啫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊會同你諗值唔值呀，買資產咩呀哥，1萬蚊買返黎玩使唔使諗值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fef16a5399d32ee387de027491b632ff32c3b40","tid":400871,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又黎話有錢人點點點，講撚到口臭<br />\n<br />\n其實有錢人真係唔會諗果d咩部5定6仲用到而考慮換唔換。1萬對佢地黎講唔係錢黎，純粹想買黎玩下，岩用就用唔岩就擺埋一邊。<br />\n<br />\n唔會似d窮撚考慮咁多，又要諗依家用緊呢部性能，又要問下依家用緊部機收幾錢</blockquote><br />\n有錢人根本唔會咁撚得閒去煩呢啲嘢<br />\n大把我識嘅<br />\n買撚咗部iPhone 5<br />\n一日唔壞一日都唔會諗新電話<br />\n你嗰啲所謂有錢人<br />\n其實可能只係中產嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該話<br />\n1萬蚊幾實好多人都負擔得起<br />\n但問題係你自己覺得值唔值啫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊會同你諗值唔值呀，買資產咩呀哥，1萬蚊買返黎玩使唔使諗值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講呢種唔係普通幾百萬年薪嘅有錢人負擔得起嘅思想，最少都要有返1億年收入先掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426965a88b9c8dcc1179d1a1c84af7933896359d","tid":400871,"uid":29942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人上淘寶買電自己換？  是否玩命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近淘寶買左粒拆機電，等緊運黎自己換，希望唔會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces